            "id": 5938075,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉「關稅豁免」反彈500多點白忙一場 台積電帶頭翻黑跌15點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (14) 日在美國豁免資通訊產品的對等關稅激勵下，早盤一度大漲近 500 點、站回 2 萬點大關，不過，外電最新報導美國總統川普 13 日駁斥「關稅豁免」是假新聞，大盤漲幅回吐、台積電承壓影響，終場翻黑下跌 15.68 點，收 19513.09 點，今日成交金額 4615 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/OTC01\">櫃買指數</a>持穩收紅，上漲 3.67 點收 208.61 點，上市櫃上漲家數超過 1500 家、下跌家數約 660 家。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股表現來看，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 今日開盤一度攻上 900 之上，但隨著賣壓湧現翻黑，終場下跌 24 元或 2.7%，收 865 元、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲 1%；高價 IC 設計指標股祥碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5269:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5269\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5269-TW</a>) 收漲停、矽力 *-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6415:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6415\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6415-TW</a>) 也攻上漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而被視為關稅豁免最大受惠這的電子代工族群，今日也多有表態，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 雖然漲幅收斂，但仍收漲近 3%、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2352:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2352\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2352-TW</a>) 漲半根停板，緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>)、仁寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>) 均漲逾 7%，電子零組件指標如川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>) 漲近 9%、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>) 漲 8%、貿聯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3665:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3665\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3665-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 也漲 6%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，貨櫃海運三雄同步上攻，萬海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2615:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2615\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2615-TW</a>) 漲停、陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>) 漲逾 7%，長榮 (2503-TW) 也收紅。不過，今天正新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2105:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2105\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2105-TW</a>) 跌 3%、漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>)、遠傳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4904:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4904\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4904-TW</a>)、統一 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1216:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1216\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1216-TW</a>) 等也跌逾 2%，為今日較弱勢指標。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
